								//stereoWidget->ImageResize(sonyTvParams[4],sonyTvParams[5]);
								//stereoWidget->getImage()->fill(Qt::black);
								//if (sonyTvParams[6]==1)
								//stereoWidget->showFullScreen();
								//stereoWidget->show();
								customBox2[0] = 0;
								customBox2[1] = 0;
								//	customBox2[2] = stereoWidget->width();
									//customBox2[3] = stereoWidget->height();
									//stereoWidget->setCustomBox(customBox2);
									//VWidget->Interactor->SetSideBySideWidget(stereoWidget);
									//stereoWidget->animMode = true;
